c: 4
v: 172
t: "Masiic (Nabii Qiisa kinnuk) Yallih Naqasu yakkeemik inkinnah isi Nafsi fayya mahaay mayaynaba, Yallat xayih tan malayka Yallih Naqoosa yakkeenimik inkinnah sinni mayaynaban, Yallih Qibaadak ise fayya haah kaxxamariinita mari, toysa Yalli Qhiyaamah Ayró inkih ken gaaboyse-le Cisab kee galtoh"